description: After shaping an impressive culinary career cooking for various highly acclaimed New York restaurants, Sara Lechman has taken on a new name and claim to fame. Now Miss Meatball is rolling through Western Pennsylvania and providing the people with a delicious assortment of gourmet chicken, beef, and pork meatballs.  There’s a bounty of balls to choose from, a few include the Classic with tomato sauce, the asian-inspired Bahn Meatball, Chicken Asiago, Mushroom Lovers, and spicy buffalo Bleu Balls too. Whether you want them bare or in a sandwich is up to you. For all this and much more, come visit Miss Meatball (or you can invite this trailer to come out and cater your next big event) and have yourself a ball!
name: Miss Meatball
